The Mikami clan of Mikami Shrine was a group based in {{ill|Mikami|ja|三上郷|12=draft}}, Yasu District, Ōmi Province. This clan served as the priestly lineage of {{ill|Mikami Shrine|ja|御上神社|12=draft}}, historically tied to {{ill|Mount Mikami|ja|三上山|12=draft}}.

Mikami Shrine claims the clan descends from {{ill|Amaterasu|ja|天照大神|1=Amaterasu|lt=Amaterasu Ōmikami|12=draft}}'s third son, {{ill|Amatsuhikone|ja|天津彦根命|12=draft}}, and his descendant {{ill|Ame no Mikage no Kami|ja|天之御影神|12=draft}}, who is said to have descended to Mount Mikami. 

