'''Mikami clan''' (三上氏) was a historical {{ill|Japanese clan|ja|日本の氏族|12=draft|12=draft}}.

== Mikami clan of Mikami Shrine ==
{{日本の氏族 (古代氏族)
|氏名 = Mikami clan of Mikami Shrine
|image = 
